title: Introducing the Nike Zoom Air Pegasus: Fast Just Got Faster
description:
Speed elites Melissa Bishop and Mo Farah put the new Zoom Air Pegasus 31 through the ringer, so we could deliver even more speed. The next chapter in the future of fast has begun. 

Learn more at http://www.nike.com/pegasus
